    <p class="note">
        On a small note, a whole poem wouldn’t fit, so I found a way.<br>
        I’d rather just leave the poem in its translated version.<br>
        I don’t like how it sounds in English.
    </p>
    
    <p class="poem">
        Мне хочется на кровать.  
        Мне хочется  
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Темноты.  
        
        Я очень люблю спать,  
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Ведь мне  
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Снишься ты.  
    </p>

    <p class="footer-text">
        I thought for a long time and didn’t know which poem to choose, but I ended up with the one you’ve already seen and know.<br>
        If I don't write that I love you, it will look like a postcard from a friend, as if<br><br>
        so... love you, Sunshine. Loved you from day one to this day.
    </p>
